snippet.title: Death's Gambit - Features Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/deaths-gambit-ps4/

As an agent of Death bound to his service, unravel the mystery of Siradon and discover the true price of immortality. Death's Gambit is coming to PlayStation 4 on August 14, 2018.
